    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="duk.00484.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Studio</name>
                    <date when="1891-07-08">July 8. 1891</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Our Brother&#8212;Friend truly</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Your note / enclosing 2 dollars to Han<ptr target="n7033"/>&#8212;directly rec'd.<ptr target="duk.00484_n1"/> She is
                better, and resolute, but very attenuated&#8212;Dr<ptr target="loc.04801_n5"/> has sent her a tonic (iron too much) 
                she went to the corner and chatted with an old neighbour<ptr target="n5001"/> this morning&#8212;had a dinner 
                of beefsteak&#8212;potates&#8212;cooks for herself&#8212;&#8212;talks of you&#8212;when 
                she shall write to you, to thank you for all years of tribute to her&#8212;mitigating pain, 
                Would like to live near to you&#8212;could walk well enough to come to you&#8212;hard 
                world this Walt. Who cares! Nobody&#8212;not one&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Gratefully Yours</salute>
                <signed rend="left">Charlie&#8212;</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
